# Per-build verifier reports. One representative green-state report per
# plan is committed alongside the verifier (see Phase 122 P03, Phase 123
# P03). Subsequent local `npm run build` runs emit fresh-timestamped
# copies that should stay untracked — gitignoring the pattern does NOT
# untrack the already-committed baselines.
.planning/reports/sitemap-determinism-*.json
.planning/reports/vs-overlap-*.json
.planning/reports/vs-wordcount-*.json